{
  "stem": "9503.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother got a job right away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had to split mica into real, real thin shape.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still have some actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the better you produced, the more-- the less chance you had of losing that job.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The kind of work you did in a camp was always very important, whether it was essential work or not.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father never even got a job in that camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was nothing available, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember that I started not feeling good again in this camp and being very dizzy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And walking with my father and talking about this, and he said, don't tell mommy because she'll worry about you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I didn't tell mommy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then in the end of September, they started sending people on transports.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And first they send all the men, and that included my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And then they asked for-- they asked for volunteers of women and children to follow their husbands and the fathers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were actually some cards that arrived that said come and join us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But apparently my mother and father had made a pact that we were going to try to stay.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were two expressions-- East and Poland was mentioned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But East was a word that really, you know, had a ring to it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The transport East-- nobody wanted to be on that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It just had bad vibes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People would volunteer to go to Bergen-Belsen and to Theresienstadt-- anything to stay off of transport East in Westerbork in that camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just remember the feeling that went with the words of nobody wanted to be on a transport East.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now in Theresienstadt, Theresienstadt, even for the Jews during the war, had this connotation of being better than other places.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
